metadata.name: MORNING OF TOTs
metadata.description:
ToT is an extraterrestrial race that has physical feats different from those of humans. They are extremely advanced in science and technology, while their culture is based on strongly developed ethics and morals. ToTs are the embodiment of a perfectly harmonic world where negativity is absent and rules are completely obsolete because of their redundancy. Their bodies are ergonomically shaped in a special and meaningful way for their culture. ToT exist in harmony with the environment and appear as important protectors of nature and ecosystems of their home planet.

There are 4 worlds belonging to the ToT race that live in my imagination, each representing a part of a day cycle, that being Morning, Afternoon, Evening and Night.
